<L>__{interior reggie's room late afternoon}
<A>__{from adam's angle. tex sits in the armchair, staring at camera. next to him is the airlines bag, its contents dumped on the floor.}
<B>__{another angle}
<A>__{including adam as he enters, his gun trained on tex. without speaking he goes to the airlines bag, then stoops down to go through the spilled contents, keeping one eye all the time on tex. but he can't find what he's looking for.}
<C>__{adam}
<P>__{(quietly)}
<D>__{all right where's the letter?}
